  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>For those who prefer not to fly, Inghams is offering late deals on the snow train to resorts across the Alps, with departures from London St. Pancras, Ebbsfleet and Ashord International.</p>
<p>With this weekly service, guests can travel by Eurostar on a Saturday and transfer direct to resort. Sit back and enjoy a relaxing rail journey across Europe on one of Inghams’ daytime or overnight services. Take advantage of the many benefits to travelling by train and choose from a range of resorts in France, Austria, Switzerland and Italy.</p>
<p>Travel by snow train and enjoy:</p>
<ul style="list-style: disc outside 1em; list-style-position: outside; margin-left: 2em; padding-left: 1em; text-indent: -0.75em;">
<li>• Free ski carriage (one set of skis per person)</li>
<li>• A larger luggage allowance compared to flying (each guest is allowed two bag plus hand luggage)</li>
<li>• Food included</li>
<li>• Free wifi</li>
<li>• Reduced check-in time compared to flying (please allow at least 60 minutes for check-in)</li>
<li>• Spacious travel</li>
<li>• Short transfers to resort</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p>Late deals by ski train include:</p>
<p>Inghams is offering a seven night holiday on a self-catering basis at the two-and-a-half star Val Claret Apartments in Tignes, France, from £469 per person, based on four sharing. Price represents a saving of £300 per person and includes return train travel from London St. Pancras. The package is valid for travel departing on 18th February 2017 and is subject to availability. To book, call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p>Inghams is offering a seven night holiday on a self-catering basis at the two-and-a-half star Jardins de Val / Les Verdets Apartments in Val d’Isère, France, from £529 per person, based on two sharing. Price represents a saving of £280 per person and includes return train travel from London St. Pancras. The package is valid for travel departing on 18th February 2017 and is subject to availability. To book, call 01483 791 114.</p>
</div>
<p>ENDS.</p>
<p>For bookings please visit <strong>www.inghams.co.uk </strong>or call <strong>01483 791 114.</strong></p>
<p>For PR enquiries please contact <span class="s1">Frankie Gibson</span>, PR Executive, frankie.gibson@inghams.co.uk or call <strong>01483 791 045</strong>.</p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
